Ramon, hei!
Apa khabar?

3
00:02:43,783 --> 00:02:46,118
Apa khabar?

4
00:02:46,243 --> 00:02:48,245
Disana, atas meja sana.

5
00:02:48,329 --> 00:02:51,624
